    - target: {fileID: 7531631086363815231, guid: b587921eb8b264a4799a34bbdb5218e0, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: In the spring of 2026, Kerem Hasan will take the podium in his new role
        as permanent guest conductor. This fulfills a wish of the NNO board, orchestra
        members, and a great many concertgoers. For Hasan endeared himself to the
        audience during his first NNO performance in 2018. Since then, the bond has
        only grown stronger.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7531631086363815231, guid: b587921eb8b264a4799a34bbdb5218e0, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_fontSize
